column5:
VAR datesel = SELECTEDVALUE( s_Switch_Calendar_Fiscal[Selection], "Calendar" )
VAR timecalc = SELECTEDVALUE( s_TimeCalc[Selection] )

-- Precompute once (both Calendar and Fiscal, cheap)
VAR LastYM_C = MAX( s_Period[Year Month Seqnr] )
VAR LastYM_F = MAX( s_Period[Fiscal Year Month Seqnr] )
VAR LastQ_C  = MAX( s_Period[Year Quarter Nr] )
VAR LastQ_F  = MAX( s_Period[Fiscal Year Quarter Nr] )
VAR MaxY_C   = MAX( s_Period[Year Nr] )
VAR MaxY_F   = MAX( s_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] )
VAR MaxM_C   = MAX( s_Period[Month Nr] )
VAR MaxM_F   = MAX( s_Period[Fiscal Month Nr] )

RETURN
SWITCH(
    TRUE(),
    
    ------------------------------------------------
    -- Calendar logic
    datesel = "Calendar",
        SWITCH(
            TRUE(),
            timecalc = "MTD", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Month Seqnr] = LastYM_C ),
            timecalc = "QTD", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Month Seqnr] <= LastYM_C && d_Period[Year Quarter Nr] = LastQ_C ),
            timecalc = "YTD", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C && d_Period[Month Nr] <= MaxM_C ),
            timecalc = "YTG", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Month Seqnr] > LastYM_C && d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C ),
            timecalc = "FY",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C ),
            timecalc = "Q1",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C && d_Period[Quarter Nr] = 1 ),
            timecalc = "Q2",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C && d_Period[Quarter Nr] = 2 ),
            timecalc = "Q3",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C && d_Period[Quarter Nr] = 3 ),
            timecalc = "Q4",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Year Nr] = MaxY_C && d_Period[Quarter Nr] = 4 ),
            BLANK()
        ),

    ------------------------------------------------
    -- Fiscal logic
    datesel = "Fiscal",
        SWITCH(
            TRUE(),
            timecalc = "MTD", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Month Seqnr] = LastYM_F ),
            timecalc = "QTD", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Month Seqnr] <= LastYM_F && d_Period[Fiscal Year Quarter Nr] = LastQ_F ),
            timecalc = "YTD", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F && d_Period[Fiscal Month Nr] <= MaxM_F ),
            timecalc = "YTG", CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Month Seqnr] > LastYM_F && d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F ),
            timecalc = "FY",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F ),
            timecalc = "Q1",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F && d_Period[Fiscal Quarter Nr] = 1 ),
            timecalc = "Q2",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F && d_Period[Fiscal Quarter Nr] = 2 ),
            timecalc = "Q3",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F && d_Period[Fiscal Quarter Nr] = 3 ),
            timecalc = "Q4",  CALCULATE( [PL-AMT-TC0 Reported], d_Period[Fiscal Year Nr] = MaxY_F && d_Period[Fiscal Quarter Nr] = 4 ),
            BLANK()
        ),

    BLANK()
)
column6:
VAR vNominatorline = SELECTEDVALUE( s_ReportLines[Nominator element] )
VAR vNominator_element =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES('s_Formulas Combined'[Formula Element] ),
        's_Formulas Combined'[Formula Header] = vNominatorline
    )
VAR vDenominatorline = SELECTEDVALUE( s_ReportLines[Denominator] )
VAR vDenominator_element =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES('s_Formulas Combined'[Formula Element] ),
        's_Formulas Combined'[Formula Header] = vDenominatorline
    )
VAR vNominator = CALCULATE( [BAL-AMT- prep Current Month], TREATAS( vNominator_element, 'd_BS_PL_CF'[Line] ) )
VAR vDenominator =
    IF(
        ISBLANK( vDenominatorline ),
        1,
        CALCULATE( [BAL-AMT- prep Current Month], TREATAS( vDenominator_element, 'd_BS_PL_CF'[Line] ) )
    )
VAR vResult = DIVIDE( vNominator, vDenominator )


RETURN
vResult
